                "invention-title": [
                    "Resource utilization system and method for abandoned strip mine",
                    "废弃露天矿的资源化利用系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "A pit lake is arranged at the bottom, an overwater photovoltaic power station is arranged on the lake surface, a water electrolysis hydrogen production system is arranged on a first flat plate on the edge of the pit lake, a hydrogen storage tank is connected to the first flat plate, and a plurality of second flat plates are arranged on the first flat plate upwards along the slope surface. A photovoltaic power station is arranged on the second flat plate, and a wind power station and a photovoltaic power station are arranged on the slope top outside the mine pit. A resource utilization method of an abandoned strip mine comprises the following steps: cleaning and shaping a mine pit, reinforcing and supporting the slope surface of the mine pit, reclaiming the unutilized blank place of the mine pit into a forest grassland, and constructing a wind power station at the top of the slope; photovoltaic power stations are built on the second flat plate and the slope top, an overwater photovoltaic power station is built in the pit lake, and a water electrolysis hydrogen production system and a hydrogen storage tank are built on the downwind side. According to the method, various resources of the abandoned strip mine are effectively utilized, ecological restoration of the mine area is completed, and economic benefits are obtained by selling green electricity and hydrogen products."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了废弃露天矿的资源化利用系统及方法，底部设置有矿坑湖，湖面上布置有水上光伏发电站，矿坑湖边上的第一平盘设置有水电解制氢系统，且相连有氢气储罐，第一平盘沿坡面向上设置多个第二平盘，第二平盘上设置有光伏发电站，矿坑外的坡顶布置有风力发电站和光伏发电站。废弃露天矿的资源化利用方法，对矿坑进行清理整形，对矿坑的坡面进行加固及支护，将矿坑未被利用的空白地方复垦为林草地，在坡顶建设风力发电站；在第二平盘和坡顶建设光伏发电站，在矿坑湖建设水上光伏发电站，在下风侧建设水电解制氢系统和氢气储罐。本发明有效利用了废弃露天矿的各类资源，既完成了矿区的生态修复，又通过出售绿电和氢气产品的方式获取经济效益。"
                }
